file_content.text: Sir! Imperial Infantry Division 130, at your command! What should we do with the survivors?
We can't have the Exchange thinking we've gone soft, can we? Execute them.
They will make excellent witnesses. Leave them alive.
You think you can cross Kiregan Freem? Kiregan Freem spits on you! Kiregan Freem kicks dirt in your face! Kiregan Freem chews on your corpse!
Boys! Show them that they do not mess with the Exchange! They do not mess with Kiregan Freem!
We're moving in on your position now....
We're ready for reinforcements. Send in a squad to hold this position.
